Tu itni care karta tha Prayas ke baccho ki jab mai test leta tha to Varsha aur Anahita baar baar kehti thi ki tujhe number na bataun warna tu bht datega XD. Aise hi mast rehna, abhi to ek aur saal ho tum Kanpur me, milenge to hum zaroor hi.

text:
Helo Snek !!
Kya hi memoir likhu bey tera, story book likhni chahiye, jisme abhi bht saari stories aur add karni hai. 

Bakchodi karne ka apna enthu itna equal hai isiliye sab kar paye. Tujhe aur Deb ko kuch bhi idea suggest karu, hamesha ready rahte the, warna to mai bhi bore hi ho jaata. Seriously bro itna hai gossip karne ko apne paas ki Palolem par kab 5-6 ghante nikal gaye pta hi nai chala. Trips ke imaginary plans to bht saare ready hain, bas tum taiyaar rehna. Silk Route bhi toh hai!!! Usko kaise bhul sakte hai... Similar to apan kaafi hai bas tera Sports aur Maths ke prati pyaar mere liye nahi hai.

Wo sab chhod lekin abhi tera target puri tarah se Kota hona chahiye iykwim XD.

P.S.: Acchi photos lena seekh le bhadwe, warna teri photos nahi lunga.
P.P.S.: Bangalore khulne do, apni puri bakchodi continue rakhenge.

text:
Yo Rax Bho***Kajala,

Bht saare kaand kiye hai saath me, par one of the best wo tha jisme Chingli ki cycle ka tala Mannu aur Raghav ke door par laga diya tha XD. PUBG khelte rahenge saath me to, bhulna mat!! Aur bhai yahan likh de rha taake bhulein nahi ki Raghav ne tere lamp ke saath kya kiya tha.

I got to see a really emotional side of you in these last days. Personally you are one of those guys I would really miss after IITK. Also kudos to how to manage to do magai and full maze with perfect balance.

text: Bhai kitna mushkil se conditioning camp khatam kiya tha par wo ek cheez hai jiske liye mai Adventure Club ko humesha thank karunga. EK hi trek par jaate to aur maza aata, but koi nai ab to Oracle me saath me hi hai. Aag lagani hai bc Bangalore me!!
author: Srajit  Kumar

text:
Fun fact: I'm writing this memoir while talking to you, listening to your rant about how useless you are and how amazing Nitin is. Had a lot of fun with you and Prajjwal in all the group projects. Har project me tum dono ke enthu ko kaafi effectively counter karne ki koshish kari hai maine. Aur bro ghumne ke imaginary plans to mai har samay banata rhta hu, but I'm damn serious about that northern lights ke neeche wala, bas bhaiya meri bhi kuch karao :(. FOMO ko dur karne ka sabse best tareeka hota hai actually cheeze karna, lekin tum saale mere saare plans ko mana karte rhte ho. Lekin koi nai mai to suggest karta hi rahunga plans. 

On a serious note, you are probably the most over-achiever person I know, but I never ever realized that you could have your insecurities as well. In first year I would have said - "Batra itna fodu hai lekin hai bht bada chutiya", and now I can very confidently say - "Batra itna fodu hai lekin hai bht jyada humble and quite similar to me hai". Very glad that you made a very big transition in these 4 years.
author: Srajit  Kumar
